---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Marc Solé Domènech">
  <section class="mb-16">
    <img id="profile-img" src="/profile.jpeg" alt="Marc Solé Domènech" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full object-cover object-top mb-6 reveal" />
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold mb-3 reveal reveal-delay-1">Marc Solé Domènech</h1>
    <p class="text-accent text-base mb-8 reveal reveal-delay-2">Product Management Leadership</p>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4 reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <p>
        I lead product teams to build things people actually want. My work sits at the intersection of
        strategy, execution, and people — figuring out what to build, why it matters, and how to get it shipped.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm passionate about <strong>clarity</strong> — in roadmaps, in communication, in decisions.
        I write here to think out loud about product, leadership, and the craft of building great teams.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-6 reveal">Recent Thoughts</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-4">
      <li class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <a href="/blog/hello-world" class="text-sm text-neutral-800 hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          First post — what this site is about
        </a>
        <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 shrink-0">Mar 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <a href="#" class="text-sm text-neutral-800 hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          Why most roadmaps are a waste of time
        </a>
        <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 shrink-0">Feb 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <a href="#" class="text-sm text-neutral-800 hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          The PM skill nobody talks about: saying no well
        </a>
        <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 shrink-0">Jan 2026</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <a href="#" class="text-sm text-neutral-800 hover:text-accent transition-colors">
          On building product culture from scratch
        </a>
        <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 shrink-0">Dec 2025</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/blog" class="inline-block mt-6 text-xs text-neutral-400 hover:text-accent transition-colors reveal reveal-delay-2">
      All posts →
    </a>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-6 reveal">Selected Projects</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-6">
      <li class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800">Search discovery overhaul</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Rebuilt the search experience end-to-end — reduced time-to-result by 40% and lifted conversion 18% in three months.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800">0→1 B2B onboarding</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Designed and shipped a self-serve onboarding flow for enterprise customers, cutting activation time from 3 weeks to 4 days.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-800">Real-time notifications platform</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mt-1">Led the product side of a cross-platform notifications system now processing 2M+ events per day across web, iOS, and Android.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/projects" class="inline-block mt-6 text-xs text-neutral-400 hover:text-accent transition-colors reveal reveal-delay-4">
      All projects →
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="mb-16 mt-16">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-6 reveal">Now</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4 reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <p>
        Currently leading product at a Series B company in Barcelona. We're building tools that help
        operations teams move faster without sacrificing reliability.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work I'm thinking about how <strong>AI changes the PM role</strong> — not eliminates it,
        but reshapes it. The bottleneck shifts from execution to judgment.
      </p>
      <p>
        I also advise two early-stage startups on product strategy and occasionally do fractional PM work
        for teams that need senior product thinking without a full-time hire.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
